summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed from A. Schlossmacher, a Bachelor, to City of Seattle, dated the 16th day of September, 1908, to Lots Four (4), Five (5) and Six (6), Block Thirty Six (36) Burke's Second Addition; also Lots Four (4) to Nine (9) Block Thirty Nine (39) Burkes Second Addition, all in the City of Seattle.
